data.text:
Living History.

CLINTON, Hillary Rodham (born 1947).

New York, NY: Simon and Schuster, 2003. [American politics] SIGNED FIRST EDITION. Octavo (24 x 16cm), pp.xi; [3]; 562. Publisher's black quarter cloth over black paper covered boards, gilt titles to spine, dust-jacket designed by Jackie Seow, with printed price of U.S. $20.00 | Can $44.00. With two suites of photographic plates. Signed by the Hillary Clinton to the first blank. With an unused birthday card featuring Hillary Clinton loosely inserted. One of the plates has a crease from folding with an image of Bill Clinton circled in red marker pen, one page with a passage highlighted in yellow, the page corner folded over, some marks to edges. Binding and wrapper lightly creased and rubbed to top and bottom edges. Very good. Item #52701

Price: £375.00 save 50% £187.50
